{"tid":1189932,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"今日差d比2隻馬騮搶手機","createTime":"2019-06-07T05:13:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-07T09:26:20.000Z","uid":120466,"like":4,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"d3b833adea4d5e4ed6c32bd67aee7b9af614a7cd","tid":1189932,"uid":120466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T05:13:53.000Z","msg":"小弟今日行行下街玩手機個陣突然有2隻🐒一個渣電單車一個係後面camp實<br />\n🐵：力架1號 🐒：力架2號 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：me<br />\n<br />\n力架2號：部手機好靚wor<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後一手搶左我個部機 <br />\n<br />\nme: <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&gt;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&gt;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&gt;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後我扮腥腥叫希望佢地聽得明： nigga nigga nigga nigga nigga nigga nigga ! <br />\n<br />\n我旁邊d人以為我傻左冇啦啦扮腥腥 有個鬼佬仲話 ： Jesus Christ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我諗住冇機啦 部手機咁就冇左。點知個2隻monkey冇啦啦番番黎。我見到佢地就嬲9 一野飛踢落隻力架2號到。佢都掉左落架車到，可能monkey 智商低得制，feel唔到架車輕左好多，掉低左佢同伴。<br />\n<br />\n咁我拎番部手機就快快步走人 走個陣仲聽到佢大叫 you fucking racist! <br />\n<br />\n依家好驚比黑警拉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 想問下各位巴打點算好"},{"pid":"3716d270dbb8afa9833432cfbfc1088851cd1fca","tid":1189932,"uid":44689,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T05:14:44.000Z","msg":"閱"},{"pid":"b8584c74f952a2dd4934ee72e06cf64c6cbca0c4","tid":1189932,"uid":120466,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"3716d270dbb8afa9833432cfbfc1088851cd1fca","tid":1189932,"uid":44689,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T05:14:44.000Z","msg":"閱"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T05:15:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmo